item.title: CVE-2024-2742|2024-03-21T11:45:41.162Z -- planet -- igs-4215-16t2s
item.description: Operating system command injection vulnerability in Planet IGS-4215-16T2S, affecting firmware version 1.305b210528. An authenticated attacker could execute arbitrary code on the remote host by exploiting IP address functionality.
